title: Derek Trucks Band - Already Live EP [FLAC]
description: This is the Already Live EP, issued in limited release for Record Store Day (April 18, 2009). Normally I would never seed a DTB record, but given that this had a limited run I figured I'd make an exception. If you can find a copy, please go out an buy it. Regardless, go out an buy any/all of the Derek Trucks Band's other recordings. Support the artists that allow free taping and trading of their music.
